      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SON OF ZATARA (3) has a terrific record this track and trip with three wins and four placings from seven starts. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (17.31) in a Novice race last time at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. BETTER HALF (2) missed the frame last time when seventh (17.61) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Solid record at the distance winning nine races. In the mix. ZATARA STORM (1) tackled far tougher grade latest when finishing 6th over 275m at Cannington. Scored at this track in weaker company the previous run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. MAJOR ACE (7) placed here at this trip last start - cannot be ignored.",
